<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٥٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(إذا)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(جاءك)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> المصدق] <span class="c2">(٣)</span> فقال: أخرج <span class="c2">(صدقتك فأخرجها)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(فإن)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> قبل فيها ونعمت، فإن <span class="c2">(أبي)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">(قوله)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> ظهرك وقيل: اللهم <span class="c2">(إني)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span> <span class="c2">(احتسب)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span> عندك <span class="c2">(ما يأخذ مني)</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ولا <span class="c2">(تلعنه)</span> <span class="c2">(١١)</span> <span class="c2">(١٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
